'''''Gravehopping''''' ([[Slovene language|Slovene]]: ''Odgrobadogroba'') is a 2005 Slovenian film [[Film director|directed]] by [[Jan Cvitkovič]]. It was Slovenia's submission to the [[79th Academy Awards]] for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film]], but was not accepted as a nominee.<ref name="VarietySubmissionList">{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/awardcentral_article/VR1117952315.html?nav=news&categoryid=1985&cs=1|title=Oscar race counts 61 countries|publisher=[[Variety (magazine)|''Variety'']]|author=Sneider, Jeff|date=2006-10-19|accessdate=2008-06-22}}</ref><ref name="NZHeraldShortlist">{{cite web|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/location/story.cfm?l_id=34&objectid=10419560|title=Foreign language Oscar nominees announced|publisher=''[[The New Zealand Herald]]''|date=2007-01-17|accessdate=2008-06-22}}</ref>
